{"tid":603586,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[試食] 來至美國嘅Sex灣Sause(四川醬)","createTime":"2018-03-24T01:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T10:51:52.000Z","uid":37491,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e172d76c01ca39eba29fcdd17c3fa247ac4077e","tid":603586,"uid":37491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:10:48.000Z","msg":"大家好，見 Szechuan Sauce 四川醬有啲討論嘅價值，所以借左朋友嘅account 同大家分享下。<br />\n<br />\n簡介: 98年首次面世，當時係配合&rsquo;花木蘭&rsquo; 電影上映作為宣傳用途，當&rsquo;花木蘭&rsquo; 嘅宣傳期完成之後就落架。 因為Rick and Morty關係，喺舊年嘅07/10以1日限時商品回歸美國麥當勞。而係今年既2月尾，美國麥當勞宣佈將提供更多嘅四川醬。<br />\n<br />\n98 同17年嘅四川醬小弟邊撚到有福氣食到呀，但見到2月又出多次，心諗&rdquo;今次老閪都要撚到個四川醬&rdquo;。之後上左Ebay望望，見到好撚多貨就搵個比較相宜嘅買。等左兩個星期就送到門口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090354_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090354_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=b4d50830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次主角<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090355_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090355_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=3f217cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試麥樂雞醬又點可以無麥樂雞，買撚夠廿粒試。同場加映有魚柳包，其他嘅麥樂雞醬 (甜酸醬，咖哩，茄汁)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090355_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090355_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=5849ff06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港嘅Shake Shake 薯條當然要一齊充下場面啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090356_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090356_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=13461df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥樂雞醬: 甜酸醬，四川醬，咖哩，茄汁<br />\n魚柳包: 同樣都係得半塊芝士。Tartar sauce(沙律醬) 同香港大同少異，但奶味較突出。而炸魚柳嘅腥味較少，魚味較濃。 <br />\n短評: 兩者差唔多，要分高下的話會係 香港魚柳包100%，英國魚柳包105%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090645_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090645_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=ce8d806d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國甜酸醬同香港甜酸醬就差好撚遠啦。英國嘅少左種 &rsquo;加工味&rsquo;，入口有水果嘅香味(桃)，甜同酸出得相對地自然。<br />\n短評: 兩者相同嘅就只有係個名，味道會係兩款唔同既醬。(個人就偏愛香港甜酸醬)<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090357_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090357_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=f5e58c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咖哩醬無論從香氣味道都係似盒裝日式咖哩(唔辣) 再煮濃啲，之後再加MSG。<br />\n短評: 同盒裝咖哩十分相似<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090357_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090357_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=9d063213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茄汁，咪茄汁囉屌你，想點撚樣姐。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/090358_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F090358_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg&h=29ad5910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四川醬，除左關個&rsquo;木蘭&rsquo; 事之外基本上同四川係唔撚關事，最多只能夠講味道好&rsquo;華人&rsquo;。<br />\n鼻+ 入口: 以麻油味為主，加上輕微嘅蠔油 豉油味為副嘅香<br />\n味道: 仍然有麻油豉油嘅香。豉油嘅咸為主 甜味為副 再加微微嘅酸 (可能來至醋)<br />\n吞左之後有好重嘅麻油香，味蕾唔會話仲食到好重嘅味<br />\n<br />\n結論就係對於一個香港成長既人，四川醬未能夠帶到一種味道上嘅沖擊，但係對於小弟呢一類離鄉別井嘅人有一份格外嘅親切感。令我覺得除非你真係一個Rick and Morty 嘅死忠，如果唔係都無太大嘅需要為呢一個醬係快餐店出面排隊排到變on9 仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 廿粒雞加個魚柳包真係好撚飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972b019311fc9fc161d8e738209313299549c561","tid":603586,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"Ok多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601a1519da7c3bafe68ca7232fa80e031a289790","tid":603586,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96adbb7c61b68e877d85dff1fed7808f2945ba1","tid":603586,"uid":47966,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:20:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有食評可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜舊魚柳冇咁腥，魚味重啲笑撚死<br />\n唔知仲以為上緊open rice"},{"pid":"08400b1fe1de6f93dc2fcb551ef3a9241ee5ccba","tid":603586,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"上次炒到好貴<br />\n今次 星期一出 星期三去買仲有<br />\n但真係好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5607a7178c102528059f3fdc5a240b08cf91a2c","tid":603586,"uid":37491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08400b1fe1de6f93dc2fcb551ef3a9241ee5ccba","tid":603586,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"上次炒到好貴<br />\n今次 星期一出 星期三去買仲有<br />\n但真係好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"我買左10個，一個約1GBP。你美國?"},{"pid":"c96f172449534898ad703c4ccb25a192971a5c4a","tid":603586,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"上次聽講換撚到架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df310ec15f86849fd8e16ae92f8daeda6f646d64","tid":603586,"uid":1518